The task contains the 'checkpass' function;
It should take a password , and check the validity of it.

The function will return true if and only if it passes the given criterias:
at least 8 characters;
at least 6 different characters;
at least 1 digit;
at least 1 uppercase letter;
at least 1 lowercase letter;
at least 1 non-alphanumeric character

Here was used Regex , about it more detailed you can read from:
VERY IMPORTANT LINK!!!!!!
